title: Bug 19083[Navigator] Navigator 'up' enablement for 'Open in New Window'
description: Bug 19083[Navigator] Navigator 'up' enablement for 'Open in New Window'
OB: Noticethat the 'up' arrow is enabled and it will take you back to the workspace.The 'up' arrow should have been enabled when the window is created.
SR: Build F2Select a project in that contains a folder and run 'Open in New Window'. Noticethat the 'up' arrow for the Naviugator is initially disabled in the new window.From the new window, select the folder and run 'Go Into'. Hit 'back'.
